Normal Operation (with descriptive observation file)

./oifits-sim -t ./sample_data/target_epsAur.txt -s ./sample_data/MIRC_LowH.txt -obs ./sample_data/obs_epsAur.txt -i ./sample_data/MIRC.txt -a ./sample_data/CHARA.txt -o ./test.oifits

Debugging:

gdb ./oifits-sim
run -t ./sample_data/target_epsAur.txt -s ./sample_data/MIRC_LowH.txt -obs ./sample_data/obs_epsAur.txt -i ./sample_data/MIRC.txt -a ./sample_data/CHARA.txt -o /tmp/test.oifits

Debugging with OIFITS:

gdb ./oifits-sim
run -t ./sample_data/target_epsAur.txt -s ./sample_data/MIRC_LowH.txt -d ./sample_data/2008Dec10-eps_Aur.oifits -i ./sample_data/MIRC.txt -a ./sample_data/CHARA.txt -o ./test.oifits


